I applied for #SpehoraSquad ✨💋💄
Hey you guys! I’ve recently applied for @sephora ‘s influencer program: Sephora Squad. This would give me the opportunity to showcase my makeup artistry, through my content, partnering with Sephora! I believe that I would make a GREAT asset to the team! I’m personable, funny, down to earth, eager to learn, & ready to network! With your help—you could boost my chances to partake in this awesome opportunity! If you could click the link in my bio & leave a short testimonial on why you think I’d be a great candidate, why you folllow me, & how I inspire you, I would greatly appreciate it! It’ll take less then two minutes & you would be helping your girl out! Lol Thank you to those that have already sent yours, & thank you to those who will! If you want me to read/know what you’ve submitted, please DM it to me, I’d love to see it! 😁 Let’s get it yall! 💋
